Navigation
   hjkl
  w  word skip
  b back word skip

  dd delete line
  dw del word
  d$ to end of line
  db  del prev word
  d0 dellft of line
  u undo
  trl r redo

V  visual mode.. Highlight
shift V visual line mode keeps lines

Neovim is recommended, but follow this to share plugins etc between vim and neovim
https://vi.stackexchange.com/questions/12794/how-to-share-config-between-vim-and-neovim

